5:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aadd580d849d8587cb096e42f5b1b9920208a903","tid":716730,"uid":59425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T19:30:01.000Z","msg":"希望佢放得低，咁我就唔會比藉口自己唔放低<br />\n不過又唔會知佢放低未"}]}